<Section xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation">
  <BlockUIContainer>
    <StackPanel>
      <FlowDocumentPageViewer>
        <FlowDocumentPageViewer.Clip>
          <RectangleGeometry Rect="0,0,550,100"/>
        </FlowDocumentPageViewer.Clip>
        <FlowDocument Background="Yellow" ColumnWidth="100" ColumnRuleWidth="10" ColumnRuleBrush="Black" PageHeight="100">
          <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold">ColumnRuleBrush=Black</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph>Once upon a midnight dreary, while I pondered, weak and weary Over many a quaint and curious volume of forgotten lore- While I nodded, nearly napping, suddenly there came a tapping As of some one gently rapping, rapping at my chamber door " 'T is some visitor," I muttered, "tapping at my chamber door- Only this and nothing more." </Paragraph>
        </FlowDocument>
      </FlowDocumentPageViewer>
      <FlowDocumentPageViewer>
         <FlowDocumentPageViewer.Clip>
          <RectangleGeometry Rect="0,0,550,100"/>
        </FlowDocumentPageViewer.Clip>
        <FlowDocument Background="Yellow" ColumnWidth="100" ColumnRuleWidth="15" PageHeight="100">
          <FlowDocument.ColumnRuleBrush>
            <RadialGradientBrush>
              <GradientBrush.GradientStops>
                <GradientStopCollection>
                  <GradientStop Color="Red" Offset="0" />
                  <GradientStop Color="Blue" Offset="1" />
                </GradientStopCollection>
              </GradientBrush.GradientStops>
            </RadialGradientBrush>
          </FlowDocument.ColumnRuleBrush>
          <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold">ColumnRuleBrush=Radial gradient</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph>Once upon a midnight dreary, while I pondered, weak and weary Over many a quaint and curious volume of forgotten lore- While I nodded, nearly napping, suddenly there came a tapping As of some one gently rapping, rapping at my chamber door " 'T is some visitor," I muttered, "tapping at my chamber door- Only this and nothing more." </Paragraph>
        </FlowDocument>
      </FlowDocumentPageViewer>
      <FlowDocumentPageViewer>
       <FlowDocumentPageViewer.Clip>
          <RectangleGeometry Rect="0,0,550,100"/>
        </FlowDocumentPageViewer.Clip>
        <FlowDocument Background="Yellow" ColumnWidth="100" ColumnRuleWidth="10" PageHeight="100">
          <FlowDocument.ColumnRuleBrush>
            <VisualBrush>
              <VisualBrush.Visual>
                <Button />
              </VisualBrush.Visual>
            </VisualBrush>
          </FlowDocument.ColumnRuleBrush>
          <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold">ColumnRuleBrush=VisualBrush</Paragraph>
          <Paragraph>Once upon a midnight dreary, while I pondered, weak and weary Over many a quaint and curious volume of forgotten lore- While I nodded, nearly napping, suddenly there came a tapping As of some one gently rapping, rapping at my chamber door " 'T is some visitor," I muttered, "tapping at my chamber door- Only this and nothing more." </Paragraph>
        </FlowDocument>
      </FlowDocumentPageViewer>
    </StackPanel>

  </BlockUIContainer>
</Section>